VI'm going to share with you a paradigm-shifting perspective
p4
aVon the issues of gender violence: sexual assault, domestic violence,
p5
aVrelationship abuse, sexual harassment, sexual abuse of children.
p6
aVThat whole range of issues
p7
aVthat I'll refer to in shorthand as "gender violence issues,"
p8
aVthey've been seen as women's issues that some good men help out with,
p9
aVbut I have a problem with that frame and I don't accept it.
