aa(lp194
VBut one of the powerful roles that men can play in this work
p195
aVis that we can say some things that sometimes women can't say,
p196
aVor, better yet, we can be heard saying some things
p197
aVthat women often can't be heard saying.
p198
aVNow, I appreciate that that's a problem, it's sexism, but it's the truth.
p199
aVSo one of the things that I say to men,
p200
aVand my colleagues and I always say this,
p201
aVis we need more men who have the courage and the strength
p202
aVto start standing up and saying some of this stuff,
p203
aVand standing with women and not against them
p204
aVand pretending that somehow this is a battle between the sexes
p205
aVand other kinds of nonsense.
